    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>garam masala</strong>,<strong> ground fenugreek</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
