    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the dal is cooking, add the <strong>blanched</strong> <strong>almonds</strong> to a baking tray and put them in the oven for 5 min or until they've darkened slightly in colour</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Once done, set them aside to cool before chopping roughly</p>",
